<br />

<br />
I will reply to this since it is most likely directed at me. First of all the thread had a loaded title at the start. This is a game message board not a political message board. I read all the crap people were posting about Regan, and I injected some truth into the thread, and my opinions on him, from the many books, and things I know about him which conflicts with the "america's greatest" thread title.
<br />

<br />
My suggestion is people shouldn't even be allowed to create threads like that because if one person can do it about someone they think was a great political figure then you will soon have people saying Stalin, Hitler, Sadam, and other world figures were some of the greastest in threads on this forum. Now I am not comparing Ronald Regan to Hitler obcourse but I am saying that there are alot of retards out there that think Hitler was a great man, and if you are allowed to say one political figure was great why can't someone else? Then you get into a very gray area, and why even go down that road?
<br />

<br />
IMO this is a message board for the Magician Class in EQ, and overall a MMORPG gaming forum to some degree. When I come here I really don't want to see political garbbage on the front page. I mean if you really wanna start a flame war on a message board, politics, religion, and racial topics is truly the way to get them going; and I say why should that even happen on this type of message forum?<br />_________________<br />Wezloc
